<SUMMARY>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
SUMMARY: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
Pursuant to the Rocky Mountain Arsenal National Wildlife Refuge Act of 1992, the Refuge Manager of the Rocky Mountain
Arsenal National Wildlife Area, U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service (Department of Interior) gives notice of the agency's
intent to prepare an environmental impact statement on the Rocky Mountain Arsenal National Wildlife Refuge Comprehensive
Management Plan, Adams County, Colorado. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</SUMMARY>
